{"tid":1119810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣新聞台就係過癮］去老翻網睇劇cap圖cap片報新聞","createTime":"2019-04-22T07:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T10:25:54.000Z","uid":58552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b680d7031833f29ba5e55eae72a90ce3b0709e","tid":1119810,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:51:18.000Z","msg":"最近最熱的台劇《我們與惡的距離》昨大結局，劇中角色包括賈靜雯、吳慷仁和陳妤、林哲熹等都有自己最好的結局。但沒想到今天中天新聞卻擷取盜版片源畫片做為新聞資料，讓人驚呆，有網友指出：「世界上最遙遠的距離不是善與惡，而是我就站在你面前你卻不知道我可惡。」對此，中天尚未回應，但已悄悄的把有問題的影片從YOUTUBE下架，但所謂凡走過必留下痕跡，早有網友備份了。<br />\n<br />\n根據影片顯示，中天所引用的片源來自大陸網站「<a href=\"http://13425.COM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F13425.COM&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6rPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=8685c3de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">13425.COM</a>」，而這幾個字也「大方」地出現在中天播出的畫面中，但中天卻打上影片「翻攝自公視」，針對此事，網友紛紛回應「中天還是別作新聞了，多多播韓國瑜你們比較擅長這個」、「 那就是中天專屬資料庫的網址，台灣人不懂啦」&hellip;等等諸多留言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3kXOU6p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kXOU6p.png&h=c72f1c4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"609591cab1dd61f446ba6502c45e9042bca94b81","tid":1119810,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"香港最多只係囉宣傳海報、劇照嚟報道 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f452ca2c159d773f3b1fdcbf9f8a249e85a55e3d","tid":1119810,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"台灣變大陸唔出奇呀"},{"pid":"f1f22e1f78264c9cc17b8cf5e3d162539c949075","tid":1119810,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:18:42.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"d9eaf78d87345cc9dfd832f143ac5aa2f006fd50","tid":1119810,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:24:45.000Z","msg":"韓流發威，中天公信第一"},{"pid":"4909ffa8f660728f463a2fff0e4f75a99b63686f","tid":1119810,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:43:28.000Z","msg":"中天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761f2c29acc5ed0fe8a0c84b154dede7f91082f6","tid":1119810,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:23:58.000Z","msg":"習近平下來 韓國瑜上去 中國發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2b2e179bfaca619a679a67471e4e50fc8d873d","tid":1119810,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:25:54.000Z","msg":"中天呢啲支那公司係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}